
### ✅ ** BVA – Age Validation (Valid Range: 18–60)**

| Test Case Type | Scenario | Test Case ID      | Title              | Step ID | Step Action     | Expected Result           |
| -------------- | -------- | ----------------- | ------------------ | ------- | --------------- | ------------------------- |
| Boundary       | Age = 17 | TC\_BVA\_AGE\_001 | Just below minimum | STP\_01 | Enter age as 17 | Error: "Age must be ≥ 18" |
| Boundary       | Age = 18 | TC\_BVA\_AGE\_002 | At minimum         | STP\_01 | Enter age as 18 | Age accepted              |
| Boundary       | Age = 19 | TC\_BVA\_AGE\_003 | Just above minimum | STP\_01 | Enter age as 19 | Age accepted              |
| Boundary       | Age = 59 | TC\_BVA\_AGE\_004 | Just below maximum | STP\_01 | Enter age as 59 | Age accepted              |
| Boundary       | Age = 60 | TC\_BVA\_AGE\_005 | At maximum         | STP\_01 | Enter age as 60 | Age accepted              |
| Boundary       | Age = 61 | TC\_BVA\_AGE\_006 | Just above maximum | STP\_01 | Enter age as 61 | Error: "Age must be ≤ 60" |

