### ✅ **BVA – CVV Validation (Must be exactly 3 digits: 100–999)**

| Test Case Type | Scenario   | Test Case ID      | Title              | Step ID | Step Action       | Expected Result                    |
| -------------- | ---------- | ----------------- | ------------------ | ------- | ----------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| Boundary       | CVV = 99   | TC\_BVA\_CVV\_001 | Below minimum      | STP\_01 | Enter CVV as 99   | Error: "CVV must be 3 digits"      |
| Boundary       | CVV = 100  | TC\_BVA\_CVV\_002 | Minimum valid      | STP\_01 | Enter CVV as 100  | CVV accepted                       |
| Boundary       | CVV = 101  | TC\_BVA\_CVV\_003 | Just above minimum | STP\_01 | Enter CVV as 101  | CVV accepted                       |
| Boundary       | CVV = 998  | TC\_BVA\_CVV\_004 | Just below maximum | STP\_01 | Enter CVV as 998  | CVV accepted                       |
| Boundary       | CVV = 999  | TC\_BVA\_CVV\_005 | Maximum valid      | STP\_01 | Enter CVV as 999  | CVV accepted                       |
| Boundary       | CVV = 1000 | TC\_BVA\_CVV\_006 | Above maximum      | STP\_01 | Enter CVV as 1000 | Error: "CVV must be 3 digits only" |

